data.description: If you have been searching for in-town living with a country feel, this 4 bed/3.5 bath w/3 car garage home is waiting for you! Sitting on over a 1/2-acre lot, this turnkey property has a spacious open floor plan on the main level and a basement made for entertaining, which includes a family room, full bar, bedroom and bath. The fun and beauty does not stop there! Step out back to enjoy the beautifully landscaped backyard, large deck and patio, hot tub and impeccable view!   Other amenities include: geothermal heating and cooling system, cherry cabinets throughout home, walk-in closets, stamped concrete patio, storm shelter in basement, large storage room in lower level and storage shed in backyard.
